    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-Differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This specimen has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension remains taut, preserving the car's legendary telepathic steering rack feedback. Finished in showroom-quality paint with an interior free of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key enthusiast's dream.",
