      "description": "This is an exceptional, collector-grade example that presents as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating and completely free from stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, documented history included. It has been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage, never driven in inclement weather, and has never seen a track day. Every switch, feature, and electronic system functions flawlessly. For the discerning buyer seeking a truly flawless machine that requires absolutely no reconditioning, this car stands in a class of its own.",
